		"name": "Flawless Swordsmanship",
		"description": "Each time Royal Swordsmanship: Judgment, Black Flash, or Rush hit, they charge the [Flawless Swordsmanship] Gauge. When the gauge reaches 50% or more, it activates [Crimson Sword Dance]. When Black Flash or Rush hit, they activate the [Crimson Fury] effect.",
