	},
	"advancements": [
		"When [Flawless Swordsmanship] Gauge reaches 50%+, Black Flash and Rush become Royal Swordsmanship: Full Moon and Bloodstorm, increasing their damage by 100%. Using Full Moon or Bloodstorm removes 50% of the Gauge. When those skills hit, they inflict [Scarlet Domination] on the target. [Crimson Fury] becomes [Undying Fury]. When Sian has 1 or fewer HP, he becomes [Immortal] for 2s.",
		"The [Oath of Victory] effect is granted to the entire team at the start of the stage. Increases Dark Overload effect by 20%.",
		"The [Crimson Sword Dance] effect is enhanced. When Black Flash, Rush, Full Moon, or Bloodstorm hit they activate the [Guardian's Resolve] effect.",
